# Run simulation 2
gt_network = NetworkConverter.nx_to_gt(nx_network)
simulators = SimMartVaq(
    network=gt_network,
    ratio_honest=0.45,
    ratio_wolf=0.45,
    delta=-10,  # no acting for wolfs
    gamma=0.5,
    tau=0,  # no fintess sharing between wolfd to criminal
    beta_s=5000,
    beta_h=10000,
    beta_c=10,
    c_c=0,  # no benefits from criminals/ they still act
    r_c=10,
    c_w=10,
    r_w=10,
    mutation_prob=-0.1,  # only fermi function
)
network, data_collector = simulators.play(
    network=simulators.network, rounds=1000, radius=3
)
